      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo moved into the old house on a cold autumn evening.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 2.7
            },
            {
              "text": "The building was large and quiet, with a long history that he did not yet know.",
              "audioStart": 3.562,
              "audioEnd": 7.588
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He decided to explore the attic after he finished unpacking his boxes.",
              "audioStart": 8.45,
              "audioEnd": 12.475
            },
            {
              "text": "The space was dark and smelled of dust, but he found a beautiful mirror standing in the corner.",
              "audioStart": 13.338,
              "audioEnd": 18.1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo walked toward the mirror to look at his face.",
              "audioStart": 18.962,
              "audioEnd": 21.475
            },
            {
              "text": "He noticed that the glass was very clear, although it was covered in age and dirt.",
              "audioStart": 22.337,
              "audioEnd": 26.525
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "When he moved his head to the left, his reflection did not move at all.",
              "audioStart": 27.387,
              "audioEnd": 30.975
            },
            {
              "text": "He stood still as he watched the man in the mirror staring back at him.",
              "audioStart": 31.837,
              "audioEnd": 35.25
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "If he had been a brave man, he might have stayed there to see what happened.",
              "audioStart": 36.112,
              "audioEnd": 39.562
            },
            {
              "text": "However, Leo felt a great fear and decided that he should leave the room immediately.",
              "audioStart": 40.425,
              "audioEnd": 44.75
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He turned around and walked toward the attic door while his heart beat fast.",
              "audioStart": 45.612,
              "audioEnd": 49.325
            },
            {
              "text": "He did not look back, but he could feel the eyes of the reflection on his back.",
              "audioStart": 50.188,
              "audioEnd": 54.062
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo closed the heavy door and locked it tight behind him.",
              "audioStart": 54.925,
              "audioEnd": 57.788
            },
            {
              "text": "He wanted to be sure that nothing could follow him out of that dark attic.",
              "audioStart": 58.65,
              "audioEnd": 62.062
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He then looked through the keyhole and saw the mirror clearly.",
              "audioStart": 62.925,
              "audioEnd": 65.688
            },
            {
              "text": "His reflection was still standing there, watching the door with a cold and hungry look.",
              "audioStart": 66.55,
              "audioEnd": 71.037
            }
          ]
        }
